        "align": "left"
      },
      "visualKind": "text",
      "title": "<p><em>Are you behind on submitting your scorecards? Has the recruiter already gotten the hiring manager to DM you - pleading for you to submit your feedback to your team&#39;s hiring platform? Well... we&#39;ve got the tool for you! </em></p><p><br /></p><p><em>Introducing the Scorecard Automator 3000. Simply schedule a 30 minute meeting with the hiring manager and the automator will do the rest - generating detailed, concise, beautiful summaries that you can copy&#43;paste into your scorecard. </em></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "n-10",
      "position": {
        "x": 765.8755761217944,
        "y": -616.1652388133004
      },
      "size": {
        "width": 428.9426730932606
      },
      "style": {
        "fontSize": 23,
        "textColor": "#1a1a1a",
        "fontFamily": "roobert_pro",
        "align": "center"
      },
      "visualKind": "text",
      "title": "<p><strong><em>Important!</em></strong><em> Make sure you record the call transcript before you start. Then go candidate by candidate having a discussion on what you liked and didn&#39;t like about each.</em></p>"
    },
